milestones.description: Gholam Nousher has conceded the most runs in an innings (45) in ODIs for BAN, going past Gholam Nousher's record of 32
Minhajul Abedin's 40 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for BAN), surpassing Shaheedur Rahman's 37
Shaheedur Rahman and Minhajul Abedin's 43-run partnership is BAN's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 41 between Rafiqul Alam and Shaheedur Rahman
Raqibul Hasan and Nurul Abedin's 26-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 3 between Raqibul Hasan and Nurul Abedin
Nurul Abedin and Gazi Ashraf's 3-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 1 between Raqibul Hasan and Gazi Ashraf
Minhajul Abedin and Gazi Ashraf's 20-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 11 between Raqibul Hasan and Shaheedur Rahman
Shaheedur Rahman and Minhajul Abedin's 43-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 12 between Shaheedur Rahman and Minhajul Abedin
Gazi Ashraf has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for BAN, going past Gholam Nousher
